								<!-- bodycontent -->
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><table class="infobox" style="width:25em; text-align:left; font-size:90%">
<tr>
<th style="font-size:120%; background:#cedff2; text-align:center;" colspan="2"><b>1978 Grammy Awards</b></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<th><b>Date</b></th>
<td>February 23, 1978</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Venue</th>
<td><a href="Shrine_Auditorium" title="Shrine Auditorium">Shrine Auditorium</a>, <a href="Los_Angeles,_California" title="Los Angeles, California" class="mw-redirect">Los Angeles, California</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Host</b></td>
<td>John Denver</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center" bgcolor="#CEDFF2" colspan="2"><b>TV in the United States</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Network</th>
<td>CBS</td>
</tr>
<tr style="background:#eee;">
<td align="center" colspan="2">
<table style="width:100%; border:1px; border-collapse:collapse; background:#cedff2;">
<tr>
<td align="center" width="25%"><b><a href="1977_Grammy_Awards" title="1977 Grammy Awards">&#160;&lt; 1977</a></b></td>
<td align="center" width="50%"><b><a href="Grammy_Award" title="Grammy Award">Grammy Award</a></b></td>
<td align="center" width="25%"><b><a href="1979_Grammy_Awards" title="1979 Grammy Awards">1979 &gt;&#160;</a></b></td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p>The <b>20th Grammy Awards</b> were held February 23, 1978, and were broadcast live on American television. They were hosted by <a href="Folk_music" title="Folk music">folk music</a> legend <a href="John_Denver" title="John Denver">John Denver</a>, and recognized accomplishments by musicians from the year 1977.<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<table id="toc" class="toc">
<tr>
<td>
