</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=1978_Grammy_Awards&action=edit&section=13.php.html" title="Edit section: Pop">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Pop">Pop</span></h3>
